The paper focuses on using deep learning algorithms for autonomous driving, specifically CNNs for perception and a controller for control. This falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO), as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for the deep learning aspect. The use of a controller also suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
